### Part 1: Reference Mockup Images (PNGs/) -- The User's Design Vision

These five images are clearly screenshots from an existing e-commerce platform (likely 91mobiles.com or a similar Indian tech product aggregator) that the user has chosen as the design reference for PhoneHub's category navigation system. They establish a consistent pattern across five product verticals.

#### 1. Electronics.png
- **Layout**: Single-column vertical list with grouped sections
- **Structure**: Items listed without a section header at top (Cameras, Smart Watches, Fitness Bands, VR Headsets), then a bold section header "Gaming" followed by Gaming Consoles and Gamepads and Joysticks
- **Icon style**: Small circular icons to the left of each item, depicting the product type in color
- **Typography**: Clean sans-serif, left-aligned, consistent spacing
- **Background**: Plain white, flat/minimalist design with no borders or shadows
- **Key pattern**: Section headers act as visual dividers between sub-categories

#### 2. Accessories.png
- **Layout**: Two-column grid
- **Left column -- "Mobile Accessories"**: Headphones/Earphones, Cases/Covers, Smart Watches, Memory Cards, Speakers, Power Banks, Chargers (7 items)
- **Right column -- "Laptop Accessories"**: Pen Drives, External Hard Disks, Keyboards, Mouse, Webcams, Graphical Tablets, Laptop Batteries (7 items)
- **Headers**: Blue bold text for category titles
- **Footer navigation**: "All Mobile Accessories -->" and "All Laptop Accessories -->" links at the bottom of each column
- **Icon style**: Same small circular icons, color-coded per product
- **Design**: Clean, flat, minimalist -- consistent with Electronics.png

#### 3. Appliances.png
- **Layout**: Three-column grid
- **Column 1 -- "Home Appliances"** (blue header): Sub-divided into "Large Appliances" (ACs, Refrigerators, Washing Machines, Air Coolers) and "Small Appliances" (Geyser, Irons, Vacuum Cleaners, Air Purifiers) using bold sub-headers
- **Column 2 -- "Kitchen Appliances"** (blue header): Flat list -- Mixer Juicer Grinders, Induction Cooktops, Microwave Ovens, Sandwich Makers, Chimneys, Hand Blenders, Electric Kettles (7 items)
- **Column 3 -- "Personal Appliances"** (blue header): Flat list -- Trimmers, Shavers, Epilators, Hair Dryers, Hair Straighteners, Hair Curlers, Electric Toothbrushes (7 items)
- **Sub-category pattern**: Bold gray sub-headers within columns to group related items

#### 4. Auto.png
- **Layout**: Single-column vertical list (simplest of all five)
- **Items**: Cars (red car icon), Bikes (blue/white motorcycle icon), Scooters (yellow scooter icon) -- only 3 items
- **Visual detail**: A thin horizontal blue line visible at the top edge, possibly a header divider
- **Background**: White/off-white
- **Icon style**: Circular gray backgrounds with colored vehicle illustrations

#### 5. Computers.png
- **Layout**: Two-column grid
- **Left column -- "Categories"** (blue header): Laptops, Computers, then bold sub-header "Computer Components" with RAM, Processors (CPU), PSU, MotherBoards, Graphics Cards, Internal Hard Drives
- **Right column -- "Other Accessories"** (blue header): Bold sub-header "Computer Peripherals" with Monitors, Printers, Projectors, Routers/Modems; then bold sub-header "Audio and Video" with Home Theaters, Computer Headphones, Computer Speakers
- **Same design language**: Blue headers, circular icons, clean sans-serif, flat design

#### Cross-Cutting Design Patterns from PNGs/

| Pattern | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Color scheme** | White background, blue (#2196F3 range) for category headers, dark gray for body text, bold dark gray for sub-headers |
| **Icon system** | Small circular product-type icons, color-coded, consistently sized, left-aligned next to text labels |
| **Hierarchy** | Blue header (category) > Bold gray sub-header (sub-category) > Regular item text |
| **Grid system** | 1-column for small categories (Electronics, Auto), 2-column for medium (Accessories, Computers), 3-column for large (Appliances) |
| **Navigation** | "All [Category] -->" footer links for drill-down |
| **Style** | Flat/minimalist -- no shadows, no borders, no cards, no dark theme. This is a LIGHT-THEME category navigation system |
| **Spacing** | Consistent vertical padding between items, slightly larger gaps between sections |

